-- Zynix Premium Cheat (Blue Edition) v4.0 – Ultimate Rage & Visual Overhaul
-- Original base: NoMercy v1 by Zywtx
-- Fully reworked with advanced ragebot, modern GUI, and enhanced performance.

-- CHANGELOG v4.0:
-- + Revamped RageBot:
--   - Separate Rage FOV (0-800) for faster target acquisition
--   - Auto Stop: halts movement while shooting for perfect accuracy
--   - Target Switch Delay: customizable delay before switching to a new target
--   - Improved prediction with scalar multiplier
-- + GUI Overhaul:
--   - Full dark theme with neon blue accents, rounded controls, smooth animations
--   - Sidebar with emoji icons, collapsible sections, and status bar
--   - Hover/click sounds, slider knob glow, modern typography
-- + New Features:
--   - Streamer Mode: instantly hides all ESP and hitbox visuals
--   - No Camera Shake
--   - Disable Screen Effects (blur, bloom)
--   - Accurate R15 skeleton (all 15 bones)
--   - Box Fill option for ESP
--   - Distance in meters with proper scaling
-- + Performance & Cleanup:
--   - Memory usage optimized, all drawings properly removed
--   - Robust error handling, no global leaks
--   - Detailed comments throughout
-- ==================================================

